      "date": "2019-09-11 23:24:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWe were questioning whether mdsrate should be removed completely, and just use mdtest for all tests?  mdsrate is only ever used for Lustre, while mdtest is commonly used for all HPC filesystem testing (including IO-500), so it is unclear whether it is worthwhile to spend time & effort on improving it.",
